name:                2-
stack:               ( x1 -- x2 )
return stack:        ( -- )
string stack:        ( -- )
contexts:            stateless
category:            arithmetics

decription:          subtract two from x1.

notes:               was meant to be unnecessary because optimiser is supposed
                     to generate identical code from 2 - but as that's not
                     already happening, 2- was added for convenience
